OL,3,C'I'll do anything to make Dean proud':
OL,4,CReflecting on a legacy of kindness
OL,6,FA close friend of Dean Lowe has told
OL,7,FITV News how he hopes to spend the
OL,8,Frest of his life honouring his
OL,9,Ffriend's legacy of kindness.
OL,11,FDean and his son Charlie from Jersey
OL,12,Fwere killed in a hit-and-run while
OL,13,Fwalking together in August 2023.
OL,15,FTony Greed, who played in a band with
OL,16,FDean for 24 years, said he was "like a
OL,17,Fbrother" to him and described him "as
OL,18,Fone of the kindest people ever".
