OL,3,C'I'll do anything to make Dean proud':
OL,4,CReflecting on a legacy of kindness
OL,6,FHe explained: "I was introduced to
OL,7,FDean by Danny Bryan in 1999 when I
OL,8,Fworked at Abacus Financial Services.
OL,9,FDanny told me that Dean was a good
OL,10,Fsinger and a Manchester United fan and
OL,11,FI was delighted on both of those
OL,12,Fcounts.
OL,14,F"I had him around to mine for a jam
OL,15,Fand he was an amazing singer and
OL,16,Fguitar player. We quickly became
OL,17,Fbrothers in music and football and
OL,18,Flifelong friends.
