OL,3,C'I'll do anything to make Dean proud':
OL,4,CReflecting on a legacy of kindness
OL,6,F"He was kind, funny, intelligent,
OL,7,Farty, but also had a serious, caring
OL,8,Fside. His real talent was helping
OL,9,Fpeople.
OL,11,F"When my brother Tom died suddenly in
OL,12,F2010, he was amazingly supportive. He
OL,13,Fwas a good listener, a great friend to
OL,14,Feveryone."
