OL,3,C'I'll do anything to make Dean proud':
OL,4,CReflecting on a legacy of kindness
OL,6,FIn April 2023, Dean dressed up as a
OL,7,Fsquirrel to run the virtual London
OL,8,FMarathon and raise money for the
OL,9,FJersey Employment Trust, where he
OL,10,Fworked to help people with
OL,11,Fdisabilities and long-term health
OL,12,Fproblems.
OL,14,FKeen to carry on Dean's legacy, his
OL,15,Fcolleagues at the Trust are now
OL,16,Forganising a 'squirrel run' in his
OL,17,Fmemory.
