OL,3,C'I'll do anything to make Dean proud':
OL,4,CReflecting on a legacy of kindness
OL,6,FFundraising Manager Caroline Spencer
OL,7,Fsaid: "We wanted something fun to mark
OL,8,Fwhat would have been Dean's 50th
OL,9,Fbirthday in February. We want to see
OL,10,Fat least 50 people dressed in squirrel
OL,11,Fcostumes jogging through St Helier.
OL,13,F"We think Dean would have approved of
OL,14,Fhaving something a bit crazy in his
OL,15,Fmemory."
OL,17,FThe run will take place on Thursday 13
OL,18,FMarch and Tony explained: "I'm coming
OL,19,Fout of my comfort zone to put on a
OL,20,Fsquirrel outfit and do it for Dean.
